   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"To Apollonios, strategos of the Arsinoite nome, Herakleides division from Petaus, son of Petaus, village scribe of Ptolemais Hormou and other villages. Wealthy as designators of embankment work. For Ptolemais Hormou: Ischyrion, son of Neseus and Diodora; and for Syron: Sokras, son of Ptollion. And supervisor of the vessels: Panoupis, son of Heron and Ouaramis. And for Syron: Penneus and Penneus, son of Penneus. And supervisor of the marketplace: Pouaris, son of Ischyrion, mother Ischyriaina."</ab>
         </div>
